{
  "stem": "5188.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was operated on three times, until they finally got this colitis this thing under control.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And over the next three years or so, she was constantly in and out of hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Aunt Erna lived with us and she worked very hard at her job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was very short-tempered with us, with my sister and me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She expected us to do housework, which we weren't used to doing, because, at home, there was always some-- in Germany-- there was always someone who helped.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So it was tough, the first few years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I wasn't a happy child, even though I lost myself in school work, and I read a great deal, and I had a very vivid imagination.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Every night, I used to imagine myself someplace else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It wasn't happy at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My father missed my mother when she wasn't home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He worked very, very hard, and was usually tired when he came home at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had contact with them the first year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wrote regularly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's when I got this picture-- when we got pictures still from Germany, after we had left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a wedding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One of my cousins got married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, after that, we didn't hear from them anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, after 1940, '41, we just didn't hear from people anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were deported to Poland, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some were deported to Riga.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This, I found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, I have-- my second cousin, by the name of Otto Marx, which is-- which is not on my list of immediate family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he and I are pretty close here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He lives in the United States.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he has done a study of the Marx's family tree.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
